title: WATCH: Antonio Conte Has Absolutely No Idea Who Joey Barton Is
text:
WATCH: Antonio Conte Has Absolutely No Idea Who Joey Barton Is Fri Feb 10 2017 21:03:53   21:03:53 GMT+0000 (GMT) Ryan Sidle Ryan Sidle in football 
C helsea boss Antonio Conte is famous for his thorough and meticulous preparation but it seems the Italian's research hasn't quite made its way to Joey Barton quite yet. 
The Blues go into this weekend's trip to Burnley sitting a comfortable nine points clear at the top of the table, and there's every chance that gap could grow if other results go their way. 
But in his pre-match press conference earlier today, Conte appeared to have some problems naming any of Burnley's squad - and in particular, Barton. 
For a man with an ego the size of Barton's, this will definitely sting a little bit: Joey who? Fckin brilliant! pic.twitter.com/ZAGzMGsSnX - Geo Thomson Art (@geokoart) February 10, 2017 @geokoart @Sxdaq just for that he'll break Hazards legs
